---
title: Cal Smart Ginger-Honey Shrimp and Salmon with Jasmine Rice, Carrots and Zucchini
description: Sweet and savoury meet in this flavour-packed shrimp and zucchini stir-fry. Bold ginger sauce, zesty green onions and fragrant honey lighten up this twist on a takeout favourite.

